- `/home/aiscend/work/vibelife/apps/web/src/app/onboarding/types.ts` - Type definitions for checklist
- `/home/aiscend/work/vibelife/apps/web/src/app/globals.css` - New CSS animations (ping-slow, progress-glow, urgency-pulse)

